40:13.326 --> 40:14.826
Yes.

40:14.828 --> 40:18.062
Fine. Then if you'll excuse me...

40:54.734 --> 40:57.268
It doesn't make sense to me.

40:57.270 --> 40:59.204
Captain Montero, breach.

41:02.676 --> 41:04.876
I don't understand.

41:18.558 --> 41:21.092
It doesn't make sense to me.

41:22.362 --> 41:24.395
I don't understand how
that kind of personality

41:24.397 --> 41:26.764
